{"config":{"lang":["en"],"separator":"[\\s\\-]+","pipeline":["stopWordFilter"],"fields":{"title":{"boost":1000.0},"text":{"boost":1.0},"tags":{"boost":1000000.0}}},"docs":[{"location":"","title":"Dom\u016f","text":""},{"location":"#mkdocs-materialx-pro","title":"MkDocs MaterialX Pro","text":"<p>Production starter pro modern\u00ed dokumentaci.</p>"},{"location":"#co-je-uvnitr","title":"Co je uvnit\u0159","text":"<ul> <li>CZ / EN</li> <li>search</li> <li>command palette</li> <li>blog</li> <li>versioning</li> <li>Mermaid</li> <li>OpenAPI</li> <li>edit links</li> <li>dark-first styling</li> <li>generated indexy</li> </ul>"},{"location":"#rychly-start","title":"Rychl\u00fd start","text":"Bash<pre><code>python scripts/generate_indexes.py\nmkdocs serve\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"#diagram","title":"Diagram","text":"<pre><code>graph TD\n  A[Docs] --&gt; B[Search]\n  A --&gt; C[Blog]\n  A --&gt; D[Versions]\n  A --&gt; E[API]</code></pre>"},{"location":"blog/","title":"P\u0159ehled","text":""},{"location":"blog/#blog","title":"Blog","text":"<ul> <li>Release launch</li> <li>Design update</li> </ul>"},{"location":"blog/design-update/","title":"Design update","text":""},{"location":"blog/design-update/#design-update","title":"Design update","text":"<p>The UI uses a dark-first composition with restrained surfaces and clear code blocks.</p> Python<pre><code>def hello():\n    return \"world\"\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"blog/release-launch/","title":"Release launch","text":""},{"location":"blog/release-launch/#release-launch","title":"Release launch","text":"<p>This release focuses on coherent structure, maintenance-friendly defaults and production deployment.</p>"},{"location":"cs/architecture/","title":"Architektura","text":""},{"location":"cs/architecture/#architektura","title":"Architektura","text":""},{"location":"cs/architecture/#obsahove-vrstvy","title":"Obsahov\u00e9 vrstvy","text":"<ul> <li><code>docs/cs/</code> a <code>docs/en/</code> pro jazykov\u00e9 mutace</li> <li><code>docs/blog/</code> pro \u010dl\u00e1nky</li> <li><code>docs/api/</code> pro OpenAPI</li> <li><code>docs/versions/</code> pro verze</li> <li><code>docs/assets/</code> pro JS, CSS a obr\u00e1zky</li> </ul>"},{"location":"cs/architecture/#tok-buildu","title":"Tok buildu","text":"<pre><code>sequenceDiagram\n  participant Author\n  participant Repo\n  participant CI\n  participant Site\n  Author-&gt;&gt;Repo: push Markdown\n  Repo-&gt;&gt;CI: GitHub Actions build\n  CI-&gt;&gt;Site: publish static docs</code></pre>"},{"location":"cs/components/","title":"Komponenty","text":""},{"location":"cs/components/#komponenty","title":"Komponenty","text":""},{"location":"cs/components/#stranky","title":"Str\u00e1nky","text":"<ul> <li>landing</li> <li>guide</li> <li>blog</li> <li>API</li> <li>versions</li> </ul>"},{"location":"cs/components/#ui","title":"UI","text":"<ul> <li>syntax highlighted code blocks</li> <li>admonitions</li> <li>tabs</li> <li>tables</li> <li>palette overlay</li> <li>language switch</li> </ul>"},{"location":"cs/faq/","title":"FAQ","text":""},{"location":"cs/faq/#faq","title":"FAQ","text":""},{"location":"cs/faq/#je-to-staticke","title":"Je to statick\u00e9?","text":"<p>Ano.</p>"},{"location":"cs/faq/#je-tam-search","title":"Je tam search?","text":"<p>Ano.</p>"},{"location":"cs/faq/#jdou-pridat-dalsi-verze","title":"Jdou p\u0159idat dal\u0161\u00ed verze?","text":"<p>Ano, p\u0159es <code>mike</code>.</p>"},{"location":"cs/getting-started/","title":"Start","text":""},{"location":"cs/getting-started/#rychly-start","title":"Rychl\u00fd start","text":""},{"location":"cs/getting-started/#instalace","title":"Instalace","text":"Bash<pre><code>pip install -r requirements.txt\npython scripts/generate_indexes.py\nmkdocs serve\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"cs/getting-started/#build","title":"Build","text":"Bash<pre><code>mkdocs build --strict\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"cs/getting-started/#doporuceni","title":"Doporu\u010den\u00ed","text":"<ul> <li>uprav <code>site_url</code></li> <li>uprav <code>repo_url</code></li> <li>dopl\u0148 vlastn\u00ed obsah</li> <li>spus\u0165 GitHub Actions deploy</li> </ul>"},{"location":"cs/reference/","title":"Reference","text":""},{"location":"cs/reference/#reference","title":"Reference","text":""},{"location":"cs/reference/#soubory","title":"Soubory","text":"<ul> <li><code>mkdocs.yml</code></li> <li><code>requirements.txt</code></li> <li><code>scripts/generate_indexes.py</code></li> <li><code>.github/workflows/deploy.yml</code></li> </ul>"},{"location":"cs/reference/#poznamka","title":"Pozn\u00e1mka","text":"<p>Tento starter je navr\u017een\u00fd pro dlouhodobou \u00fadr\u017ebu a jednoduch\u00e9 roz\u0161i\u0159ov\u00e1n\u00ed.</p>"},{"location":"cs/api/","title":"API","text":""},{"location":"cs/api/#api-dokumentace","title":"API dokumentace","text":""},{"location":"cs/features/","title":"Funkce","text":""},{"location":"cs/features/#funkce","title":"Funkce","text":"Funkce Stav Fulltext search p\u0159ipraveno CZ / EN p\u0159ipraveno Auto index p\u0159ipraveno Blog p\u0159ipraveno Versions p\u0159ipraveno Mermaid p\u0159ipraveno OpenAPI p\u0159ipraveno Edit on GitHub p\u0159ipraveno Ctrl+K palette p\u0159ipraveno Lazy loading p\u0159ipraveno Skeleton loading p\u0159ipraveno"},{"location":"en/","title":"Home","text":""},{"location":"en/#mkdocs-materialx-pro","title":"MkDocs MaterialX Pro","text":"<p>Production starter for modern documentation.</p>"},{"location":"en/#included","title":"Included","text":"<ul> <li>CZ / EN</li> <li>search</li> <li>command palette</li> <li>blog</li> <li>versioning</li> <li>Mermaid</li> <li>OpenAPI</li> <li>edit links</li> <li>dark-first styling</li> <li>generated indexes</li> </ul>"},{"location":"en/#quick-start","title":"Quick start","text":"Bash<pre><code>python scripts/generate_indexes.py\nmkdocs serve\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"en/architecture/","title":"Architecture","text":""},{"location":"en/architecture/#architecture","title":"Architecture","text":""},{"l